description.simpleText: How to Fast Before a Triglycerides Blood Test. Part of the series: Health & Nutrition. Before a triglycerides blood test, a person should fast for 12 hours by not eating or drinking foods or drinks with calories. Fast properly before a triglycerides blood test with tips from a licensed dietitian in this free video on health and nutrition.
